{"tid":142921,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"驚人數字！Pokemon GO 推出至今已捕捉 880 億小精靈","createTime":"2017-03-04T07:57:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-04T10:40:44.000Z","uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ed19cd75f93f0697f2ae1b424b97e13ad2955c0c","tid":142921,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T07:57:04.000Z","msg":"早前《Pokemon GO》推出了更新，部分玩家重拾這款去年曾經風摩一時的手機遊戲。日前開發商 Niantic Labs 的 CEO John Hanke 在 MWC 接受傳媒訪問時，公佈了一系列驚人的遊戲數據，和今年有關遊戲的新消息。<br />\n<br />\nHanke 表示自《Pokemon GO》推出以來，玩家共捕捉了 880 億隻小精靈，要達到這驕人的成績，玩家共消耗了 44PB （1PB = 1,000TB）的流動數據，玩家們的總步行距離亦達到 54 億英里（約 87 億公里）。所有平台合計的遊戲下載次數達 6.5 億，求全有超過 35,000 個零售點成為遊戲的贊助點，累計吸引了 5 億人次到訪那些地方。<br />\n<br />\n剛剛推出了第二代更新的《Pokemon GO》，Hanke 指出今年還會有至少 3 次大型更新。雖然未有進一步透露詳情，但可以肯定的是小精靈交換和玩家對戰將會是更新的主打賣點。此外，Hanke 亦透露 Niantic Labs 正在籌備《Ingress》的新版本，預計會在今年內推出。<br />\n<br />\n沒有買賣就沒有傷害<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f982f3024cd7de1347db692a7b0df6fa5b3172c","tid":142921,"uid":7555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T07:59:31.000Z","msg":"ingrees更新無人care啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d32276a423cd13e17655ad149db681badb02dc73","tid":142921,"uid":47978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T08:01:51.000Z","msg":"啲番啲廢中玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad71e444c05abf4f6f8369d9dad9eea8fd87267b","tid":142921,"uid":47978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T08:02:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得番啲廢中玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"df2edf43693fbc6243b364c90b0d8d0e25306f03","tid":142921,"uid":2861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T08:07:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ingrees更新無人care啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾可惜其實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e1e5b23a0680987585f695bce034a3e884e07c8","tid":142921,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T10:40:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>ingrees更新無人care啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾可惜其實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔可惜<br />\n咪又係捉捉捉捉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}